íŸ@475cdda97f088b621bad52c0faaadd667a10419d4c020b83591a302d9c9c4d60⁄©Title: title: math sum
Path: Examples
Content:
Sum a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [1 2 3] | math sum
6

```
Get the disk usage for the current directory.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ls | get size | math sum


```
Compute the sum of each column in a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [3 4]] | math sum
